title: Michael Moore In Trump Land Trailler HD

sources.title: Michael Moore In Trump Land Trailler HD
sources.description: Michael Moore in TrumpLand is a 2016 documentary film by Michael Moore [3] [4] [5] [6] [7] about Donald Trump . The film is based on a one-person show that Moore originally wanted to perform in Midland Theatre in Newark, Ohio on October 7, but management of the Midland Theatre chose not to go forward on a rental contract. [8] [9] [10] He eventually held the show at the Murphy Theatre in Wilmington, Ohio , with the movie based on a recording of that performance over two nights in October
